{
  "stem": "7093.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "If he had to give me an order or something, was very gruff always.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "But he was marvelous, marvelous in-- in the brakes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I was always happy if he was on because if anybody else was on I wasn't sure whether I'm going to be crushed against this iron door or not.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But with him I could be absolutely sure because he was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And from time to time he would come back-- we heard that he was a man who had seven children and was very poor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And from time to time he would come, and in his very gruff manner, would put into my hand a piece of newspaper where there was a tiny little onion in it or a tiny little piece of bread and would tell me, you go into that corner and eat it there, but give me back the paper.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "There was always something on the paper that warmed my heart.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Some little defeat or some victory or-- or something which the-- I-- and I was immensely grateful to him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "He then suddenly disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "There were rumors that he did help one of our inmates and he was sent away to Westphalia, to where they were-- on to the front.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "But, anyway, I never-- and I'm very, very sorry I could never find out his name, because I would have loved to thank him for his kindness.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Because it was really a piece of humanity in those-- in those days, for which I was very grateful.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Now, down in the offloading bay there was a Frenchman and a Ukrainian girl who were working.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And I picked up a few actually I believe Russian words and not Ukrainian words.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Perhaps she was a Russian girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
